								</extent>
								<foliation>
									<p>288 folios (+ 2 modern paper flyleaves at the beginning and at the end).</p>
								</foliation>
								<collation>
									<p>Quires of mostly 10 leaves each.</p>
									<p>Signed with Hebrew letters on the last and first page of a quire.</p>
								</collation>
								<condition>
									<p>Imperfect at the beginning and at the end.</p>
									<p>Gaps after folios 29 and 48.</p>
									<p>Stained, partly water-damaged.</p>
								</condition>
							</supportDesc>
							<layoutDesc>
